RawLine: ITEM_202057_Tip,劍鋒派掌門之劍，劍身刻有「谷岳」兩字，此劍的血溝形狀如岳似谷，劍身較厚。,剑锋派掌门之剑，剑身刻有「谷岳」两字，此剑的血沟形状如岳似谷，剑身较厚。

Items.mt: The sword of the master of the Jianfeng school, with the word "Gu Yue" engraved on its body, the blood groove of this sword is shaped like a mountain and resembles a valley, and the sword is thicker.
